{"tid":307480,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"姊妹送蛋糕串錯名？朱千雪解畫","createTime":"2017-07-03T11:44:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-06T07:15:26.000Z","uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5fb355abb273123d2406b53d0a132732c5e2e1ca","tid":307480,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T11:44:00.000Z","msg":"朱千雪（Tracy）獲好姊妹岑杏賢、湯洛雯、蔣家旻為她慶祝生日，送上特別的玻璃球生日蛋糕給她，但生日牌上她的英文名「Tracy」被寫成「Trace」，疑似串錯字。朱千雪看到大家的疑問後，留言為姊妹們解釋並沒有串錯字。她說：「蛋糕沒有串錯，Trace是Tracy的短寫，也是一路都只有家人跟好朋友才會叫我的nickname，所以這個蛋糕不但沒有寫錯，還能完完全全代表了我們的友誼。Jennifer Shum（岑杏賢）」<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20170630/s00092/92923f89b3713a1ce00db2474c638e0c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20170630%2Fs00092%2F92923f89b3713a1ce00db2474c638e0c.jpg&h=e66c0270&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n看朱千雪上載的照片，見她連日來跟不同的朋友慶祝，其中有她換上另一件衫坐在花花蛋糕前拍照，未知是否跟她那位了解中的對象慶祝呢？馬德鐘兩公婆鬥「胸」苗彤王曼喜星二代「胸」群出擊 梁家輝大女激吻男友 - 20170703<br />\n2陳柏宇夏威夷蜜月急造人 甜蜜咀嘴太太符曉薇20秒 - 201707034蔡依林大解放 Deep V泳衣騷身材"},{"pid":"a97e9d59f9d77372b8e9110bc11eeec5dee5d9b9","tid":307480,"uid":10277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T11:49:58.000Z","msg":"Trade"},{"pid":"694188323f8a4c399e06ab69ec92c7dddf1593b8","tid":307480,"uid":53105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T11:51:01.000Z","msg":"tray"},{"pid":"23e301189c44b1a93fa86025996b6eff550e43f2","tid":307480,"uid":20473,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T11:53:06.000Z","msg":"兩個都5個字母點短寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"928d563a927c9d6ae00bcbef58b60c1e2f2bdca8","tid":307480,"uid":30510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T11:55:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兩個都5個字母點短寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n夠簡體夠够啦"},{"pid":"3ef6825581e008b0ba0521af99cbdbbd6a8c030c","tid":307480,"uid":51978,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedB